Second, hehe i have to say it again Quineloe's post was a great summary how things are <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>TODAY</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>The way to becoming a better wizard and finding more groups isn't the addition of new abilities, it's mastery of the ones you already have- even the ones you overlook, as Natan and Quinloe do.<br>
