some think our damage is ok, some think its not. im in the middle. its ok, we do more damage than other classes sure (except for an upgraded ice nuke post 60), but we could also be better. since mostly what  we are about is damage we should be far better at nuking than any other caster ( and i dont mean better by a few hundred points of damage). and the better damage we have the more desirable we are in groups. <br>
